theme_override_colors/font_color = Color(0.9, 0.92, 0.95, 1)
theme_override_font_sizes/font_size = 20
autowrap_mode = 3
text = "Survive endless waves of falling enemies.

MOVE — drag anywhere, or A/D. You fire automatically at the nearest enemy.

DASH — Space or the ⟩⟩ button. You're invincible mid-dash — use it to dodge.

ELEMENTS — pick upgrade cards after each wave. Tap an element row (top-left) to switch your active attack.

ULTIMATE — once an element is maxed, fill the charge and press Q to unleash it.

BOSSES — every 10 waves. Dodge the glowing telegraph circles. Some bosses resist an element — check the cycle (top-right) and switch to the one that beats it."

